  <text>
    <textblock>Assessment of Educational Impact</textblock>
    <textblock>The Secretary particularly requests comments on whether the proposed regulations in this document would require transmission of information that is being gathered by or is available from any other agency or authority of the United States.</textblock>
    <textblock>List of Subjects in 34 CFR Part 602</textblock>
    <textblock>Colleges and universities, Education, Reporting and</textblock>
    <textblock>recordkeeping requirements.</textblock>
    <textblock>[Catalog of Federal Domestic Assistance Number does not apply.]</textblock>
    <textblock>Dated: January 14, 1994.</textblock>
  </text>
  <signer>
    <textblock>Richard W. Riley,</textblock>
  </signer>
